<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC '-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.01 Transitional//EN'>
<html>
  <head></head>
  <body>
    <% if @undertaking.user.confirmed_acspri_member? %>
      <p>Thank you for signing the ASSDA General Undertaking Agreement and requesting access to the data listed in the copy of the agreement below. Once your request has been processed you will be invoiced, and notified by email when you have been given access to the data requested.</p>
    <% else %>
      <p>Thank you for signing the ASSDA General Undertaking Agreement as an ACSPRI member. Upon confirmation of your institution's ACSPRI membership you will receive an acknowledgement email and will gain access to all unrestricted datasets.</p>
    <% end %>

    <p>Please keep this email as a copy of the agreement:</p>
    <hr />
    <%= render 'undertakings/agreement_general', :undertaking => @undertaking %>
    <br/>
    <%= render 'signature' %>
  </body>
</html>
